<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<title>jQuery-CSS3插件</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://ajax.aspnetcdn.com/ajax/jQuery/jquery-1.6.1.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../script/jquery.css3.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="prettify.js"></script>
<link href="css/common.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
<h1>jQuery.CSS3插件</h1>
<hr>
<h2>css("opacity")</h2>
<h3>概述</h3>
<p>访问第一个匹配元素的样式opacity。</p>
<p>IE下通过，如果元素设置了Alpha滤镜，则返回Alpha滤镜设置的Opacity/100</p>
<h3>示例</h3>
<code>alert($("#qqmsg").css("opacity"));</code>
<hr>
<h2>css("opacity", value)</h2>
<h3>概述</h3>
<p>在所有匹配的元素中，设置一个样式opacity的值。</p>
<p>IE9 以下或IE怪癖模式下通过jQuery.css3插件实现。</p>
<h3>可用值</h3>
<p>0-1之间的数字,0完全透明，1为不透明</p>
<h3>示例</h3>
<code>$("#qqmsg").css("opacity",0.3);</code>
<div id="demo">这里是一个示例<br>
请拖动滚动条→<br>
opacity:0.6</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
$("#demo").css({
	"background": "rgb(255,255,0)",
	"position": "fixed",
	"opacity": 0.3,
	"width": 100,
	"right": 18,
	"top": 5
});
</script>
</body>
</html>
